pull_request.title: I(ETF) interop image
pull_request.body:
Creates an image for interop testing at https://github.com/IETF-Hackathon/pqc-certificates:
- Based on ubuntu
- builds `openssl` (master)
- latest `liboqs`
- `oqsprovider` with all algorithms and [NOPUBKEY_IN_PRIVKEY](https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/oqs-provider/blob/main/CONFIGURE.md#nopubkey_in_privkey) set

Note: Not added to CI: Worthwhile? Current image deposited at https://hub.docker.com/repository/docker/openquantumsafe/oqs-ossl3/general (:interop)
